The first pipeline was written in Python3 and processes NCBI RefSeq data and carries out HMM profile construction, all-by-all HMM comparison and HMM-HMM comparison to PHROGs and ECOD databases. The second pipeline, written in R version 4.1, takes the output of the first pipeline as input and generates all outputs and figures presented in the publication.
